messages.content: Hi there! Thanks for calling EZ Mobile Mechanic. What’s going on with your vehicle today?
Got it! Could you please tell me the year, make, and model of your vehicle?
No problem! Just need the year, make, and model of your vehicle when you get a chance.
Thanks for that! Just to clarify, is it a Geo Metro from 1996? And what's the main issue you're experiencing with it?
Great! What's the problem you're having with your Geo Metro?
so the clutch went out I need a new clutch
Got it! I can text you a quick estimate for the clutch replacement. Would you like that?
